Ian Nepomniachtchi vs Liviu Dieter Nisipeanu
Dortmund Sparkassen (2019), Dortmund GER, rd 6, Jul-20 
Russian Game: Nimzowitsch Attack (C42)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Ne5 d6 4. Nf3 Ne4 5. Nc3 Nc3 6. dc3 Be7 7. Be3 O-O 8. Qd2 Qe8 9. h4 Qa4 10. h5 h6 11. Bd3 Re8 12. Kf1 Bf8 13. Nd4 Qd7 14. Rh3 Nc6 15. Rg3 Kh8 16. Nc6 bc6 17. Bd4 Re6 18. Qf4 Qe8 19. Re3

The annual Sparkassen Chess Meeting takes place from 13-21 July 2019 in the Orchesterzentrum NRW in Dortmund, Germany. The eight-player round-robin field is headed by Ian Nepomniachtchi and Leinier Dominguez.

Players receive 100 minutes for 40 moves, then 50 minutes for 20 moves, then 15 minutes for the rest of the game, with a 30-second increment from move one. Official site: www.sparkassen-chess-meeting.de
